      <abstract>This collection contains the records of the Congregational Club, fully established
        in April of 1869. This club served to create cameraderie between members of the
        Congregational community. This collection contains records through 1947, but the club
        continued to exist until it was disbanded at some point between 1978 and 1981. The
        collection contains event-related materials, administrative records, and
        necrologies.</abstract>
